node.text:
8 weeks, 40 workouts, 56 days to invest in YOU 💖 Only 4 DAYS til our new at-home challenge begins.  Are you ready to get TONED & SHREDDED cuz I ammm🙋🏼‍♀️

💸1st prize: $5k
💸2nd prize: $3k
💸3rd prize: $1k
Top the leaderboard: $1k fitness prize pack
Weekly giveaways in the 8WC Facebook group

Sign up is through the TammyFit app (link in bio, you don't need to subscribe to purchase) but you will get access to the FULL app for the duration of the challenge!! (Lots of healthy yummy recipes and meal plans 🤌🏼)

It can be done at home, all you need are dumbbells and a bench/chair (but feel free to do the challenge in the gym if you like!) if you are doing it at home I recommend dumbbells that you consider heavy that will really challenge you.  Or a variety of dumbbells is even better!  Booty bands an added bonus but aren't essential.

THIS CHALLENGE WILL ONLY WORK AS HARD AS YOU DO!! You need to be putting your FULL effort into EVERY workout & exercise.

It's getting so close so make sure you sign up now while you can💪🏼💕 Link in bio

node.text:
Still time to sign up to the 8 week tone & Shred Challenge 💪🏼 It starts NEXT WEEK!! Link in bio

In these photos, on the left I was working out a little, I was restricting my calories HUGELY, lots of cardio, I wasn't being healthy, I didn't really know what I was doing.  To the right which was today, i train consistently and effectively, i do mostly weights.  I eat SOOO MUCH beautiful healthy food in abundance (while still having treats/indulging when I want). Not to mention I had my two beautiful kids in between these as well ! This has taken YEARSS of consistent hard work and it has been a hell of a journey but I have loved every step.  The place I am in now not just physically but mentally is just incredible.  I went from being lost to being completely in love with life!! YOU CAN TOO!! It is never too late to start.  You can completely transform your life, believe that!  If you need some guidance on where to start, download the TammyFit app today or sign up to our 8 Week Tone & Shred Challenge starting NEXT WEEK!! Check out @tammyhembrowfitness for more info💖 link in bio
